N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 11 ยง 30.6 - Obligations of an authorized insurer

State Regulations

The amount of any compensation that an authorized insurer or its agent pays to an insurance producer shall be maintained by the insurer in accordance with Part 243 (Regulation 152) of this Title. Notes
